    {
      "_key": "nE9LI48Z10jx",
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "h3",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "wzlFcoNEE1BN",
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "What's Open When"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_key": "9hdsefjk3",
      "_type": "block",
      "children": [
        {
          "_key": "pm2200cw4",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": "One important piece of island reality: hours change by season, and some smaller businesses close entirely in winter. The Port Charlotte Hotel, Co-op Bowmore, Lochindaal Seafood Kitchen, and Islay's Plaice are the most reliably open year-round. "
        },
        {
          "_key": "ctz96v1xa",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "fitgcb8rl"
          ],
          "text": "An Tigh Seinnse"
        },
        {
          "_key": "253nqw7eg",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": " in Portnahaven is open year-round. Winter hours apply from November — always book ahead and confirm current hours for winter visits. The "
        },
        {
          "_key": "zp6y7dg0m",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [
            "xvrwpierv"
          ],
          "text": "Museum of Islay Life"
        },
        {
          "_key": "aoj4ja6ja",
          "_type": "span",
          "marks": [],
          "text": " is typically open April to October. We update our house notes for each property with current opening hours for local businesses — if you're arriving in shoulder season or winter, ask us when you book and we'll tell you what's operating."
        }
      ],
